## 5. LLM Provider Routing

Configured via env vars in `.env.example`:

| Purpose | NVIDIA NIM Model | Gemini Fallback |
|---|---|---|
| `text_classification` | `meta/llama-3.1-70b-instruct` | `gemini-2.5-flash` |
| `visual_analysis` | `liuhaotian/llava-v1.6-mistral-7b` | `gemini-2.5-flash` |
| `review_analysis` | `meta/llama-3.1-70b-instruct` | `gemini-2.5-flash` |
| `general` | — | `gemini-2.5-flash` |

**Env vars**: `GOOGLE_API_KEY`, `NVIDIA_API_KEY`, `LLM_PROVIDER` (auto/gemini/nvidia).

**Analyzers using LLM**: `visual_analyzer`, `review_analyzer`, `subscription_analyzer`, `pricing_analyzer`.

